OPSXP is an independent workflow layer maintained by Yung-Chih-Lo.

OPSXP depends on OpenSpec but does not vendor OpenSpec's official skills.
Install the compatible upstream CLI with:

  npm install -g @fission-ai/openspec@1.6.0

